SunOpta Foods, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 6:19 PM ET
Food Products

Company Overview of SunOpta Foods, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
SunOpta Foods, Inc. sources, processes, and distributes natural and organic food products in North America. The company’s products include organic, non-GMO, and IP soy, corn, sunflower, and whole grains; soy, dairy, and grain based ingredients; packaged products, soymilk, and consumer foods; and natural and organic fibers, fiber blends, stabilized brans, stabilized wheat germ, barley beta-glucan, specialty starches, ingredient systems, and acid whey. It also processes and packs natural and organic frozen fruits and vegetables, such as strawberries, peaches, and mangos for food service, private label retail, and industrial ingredient markets, as well as produces natural and organic apple-base...
SunOpta Foods, Inc. sources, processes, and distributes natural and organic food products in North America. The company’s products include organic, non-GMO, and IP soy, corn, sunflower, and whole grains; soy, dairy, and grain based ingredients; packaged products, soymilk, and consumer foods; and natural and organic fibers, fiber blends, stabilized brans, stabilized wheat germ, barley beta-glucan, specialty starches, ingredient systems, and acid whey. It also processes and packs natural and organic frozen fruits and vegetables, such as strawberries, peaches, and mangos for food service, private label retail, and industrial ingredient markets, as well as produces natural and organic apple-based fruit snacks. In addition, the company provides organic food solutions to food manufacturers and distributors, and supermarket chains, as well as trades organic commodities. Further, it distributes fresh produce; and dry, refrigerated, and frozen groceries in Canada, as well as offers contract manufacturing and processing services. SunOpta Foods, Inc. was formerly known as SunOpta Food Group LLC. The company was founded in 1999 and is based in Edina, Minnesota. SunOpta Foods, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of SunOpta Inc.
Detailed Description


7301 Ohms LaneSuite 600Edina, MN 55439United StatesFounded in 2013



Phone: 320-763-5977








