Products

We specialize in the sourcing, processing and packaging of natural and organic products from 'field-to-table'. We source organic and non-GMO raw materials from growers, convert these into value-added ingredients and leverage our inputs to produce consumer packaged products - creating value throughout the supply chain.




Raw Materials
Our capabilities include contracting and purchasing non-GMO and organic raw materials from growers, as well as sourcing high quality raw materials internationally. 



Ingredients
We add value to non-GMO and organic raw materials by converting these high quality inputs into a variety of food ingredients. Included in our portfolio are value-added grains, along with vegetables and fruit-based foods. 




Consumer Packaged Products
Our field-to-table portfolio includes consumer packaged products for retail and foodservice use. We consistently ensure our end products are of the highest quality and value. 



Animal Feed
We provide operational integrity and global supply chain capabilities in sourcing certified organic and non-GMO feed ingredients. 









