Raw Materials

Raw Materials
SunOpta offers a wide variety of raw materials and our diversified global ingredient sourcing and supply platform ensures the highest quality and value. Our capabilities include contracting and purchasing non-genetically modified and organic raw materials from growers, as well as sourcing high quality raw materials internationally. SunOpta's raw materials are sourced from over 60 countries and we have relationships with over 5,000 growers. We add value to the raw materials we source, turning them into a variety of food ingredients for food manufacturers.



