SunOpta Grains and Foods Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 6:19 PM ET
Food Products

Company Overview of SunOpta Grains and Foods Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
SunOpta Grains and Foods Inc. develops, produces, and supplies identity preserved, non-genetically modified, and organic grain-based ingredients for the food industry. The company provides organic soybeans, grains, liquid and spray-dried soymilk, soy flours, maltodextrins, sweeteners, vegetable oils, textured soy proteins, milled corn products, and cereal grains and flours. It exports its products to Australia, Oceania, Northeast Asia, North America, Southeast Asia, and Western Europe. The company was founded in 1978 and is based in Hope, Minnesota. As of 1999, SunOpta Grains and Foods Inc. operates as a subsidiary of SunOpta Inc.


3824 SW 93rd StreetHope, MN 56026United StatesFounded in 1978



Phone: 507-451-4724

Fax: 507-451-2910








